summary: Jude Law Officially Confirmed as Yon-Rogg in Captain Marvel
title: Jude Law Officially Confirmed as Yon-Rogg in Captain Marvel
body:
Jude Law Officially Confirmed as Yon-Rogg in #CaptainMarvel

Even though it’s been leaked with every single piece of merchandise released so far, Marvel has kept Jude Law’s role in Captain Marvel a secret…untul now.

In a new featurette Marvel just released about the movie, he is officially confirmed to be Yon-Rogg. All of that Mar-Vell stuff was a classic Marvel misdirection as Law is not playing that character in the movie.

You can see the featurette…
